                            <comment id="17554629" author="kwin" created="Wed, 15 Jun 2022 14:31:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This error is caused by the fact that the &lt;tt&gt;NodeTypeValidator.validateJcrPath(...)&lt;/tt&gt; is incorrectly called with value &lt;tt&gt;true&lt;/tt&gt; for parameter &lt;tt&gt;isDocViewXml&lt;/tt&gt; for the non-docview xml file.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17555657" author="kwin" created="Fri, 17 Jun 2022 15:15:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/commit/45711185f567dc63e61619a7f551f172fff8d6dc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/jackrabbit-filevault/commit/45711185f567dc63e61619a7f551f172fff8d6dc&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

